{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 1724, "height": 2350, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "补叙杜氏宗谱杜坑、孟村、西窑三门序", "block_bbox": [431, 275, 1427, 339], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "杜坑、孟村、西窑三门，皆系由西村本宗迁出。因世远年湮，与本宗失去连系，或因世变迭更，子孙凋零，并其先祖名讳亦多失传。然幸尚能知其确由西村本宗迁出，而世次尚不至紊乱者。今当续谱之际，咸有首丘依风之感。因并补叙，使已误于前者，不致再误于后，以遂其木本水源之思，而敦族谊于无穷云。", "block_bbox": [287, 399, 1576, 613], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [145, 632, 211, 1222], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十五世卿云序公元一九六二年元月", "block_bbox": [1193, 628, 1532, 723], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "义马市杜坑", "block_bbox": [730, 893, 1115, 956], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "杜坑村位于义马市新区办事处梁沟社区青龙山南麓，同梁沟村与侯岭村三足鼎立。杜姓十世杜银、杜金兄弟二人约于清乾隆年间携家居住，杜坑村因此而得名。杜姓定居杜坑后，以农耕为生，繁衍生息下传十二世。杜姓人勤农耕，重教育，习礼仪，为人宽厚，处事公道，忠诚善良，有良好的家风。除居住杜坑村外，亦有迁往义马市石门村、裴村、马岭村、卢氏县城关、陕西省韩城市、河北省石家庄市等地居住，人财两旺，发展较快。\n", "block_bbox": [288, 1013, 1575, 1330], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "其世系为：", "block_bbox": [366, 1346, 529, 1384], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "流芳公——失传——失传——失传——失传——失传——失传——失传—檀—银、金\n", "block_bbox": [291, 1397, 1572, 1495], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "二七一", "block_bbox": [159, 1758, 203, 1850], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 9}], "layout_det_res": {"boxe